          </list-item>
          <list-item>
            <p>Thickening: Thickening extending through the entire leaflet (5 mm to 8 mm)</p>
          </list-item>
          <list-item>
            <p>Calcification: Brightness extending into the mid portions of the leaflets</p>
          </list-item>
